                        <strong>"How to Live Financially Free & Secure"</strong>
                    </p>
                    <p>He is best-known as the author of <i>Rich Dad Poor Dad</i> &mdash;the <strong>#1 personal finance book of all time</strong>. With more than 30 million copies sold, Robert Kiyosaki has challenged and changed the way tens of millions of people around the world think about money.  He is an entrepreneur, educator, and investor who believes that each of us has the power to make changes in our lives, <strong>take control of our financial future</strong>, and <strong>live the rich life we deserve</strong>! Robert has earned an international reputation for straight talk about money and has become a passionate and outspoken <strong>leader in financial education</strong>.</p>

                    <p>The author of 29 books, Robert has been a featured guest with media outlets in every corner of the world&mdash; from: FOX News, CNN, the BBC, Real Vision, Yahoo! Finance, Al Jazeera, GBTV and PBS to <i>Larry King Live, Oprah, Peoples Daily, Sydney Morning Herald, The Doctors, The Straits Times, Bloomberg, NPR, USA TODAY, and hundreds of others</i>&mdash; and his books have topped international bestseller lists for more than two decades. He continues to teach and <strong>inspire audiences</strong> around the world.</p>

                    <p>In his powerful session, Robert will teach you <strong>live-and-in-person</strong> everything you need to know in 2020 to take your finances to new levels of success:</p>

